PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774012289
OL,3,CFamily of murdered teenager vow to
OL,4,Cmatch #20,000 reward for information
OL,6,FOn Wednesday 18 March, Carolyn Cox,
OL,7,FEllis' mum announced that the family
OL,8,Fwill match the #20,000 reward that
OL,9,Fwould lead to a conviction, making
OL,10,Fdoubling the total reward to #40,000.
OL,12,FCarolyn Said: "If anybody has anything
OL,13,Fto help us with, it is what we need."
OL,15,FShe added: "From me, as Ellis' mum, I
OL,16,Fwould beg anybody ` their parents,
OL,17,Ftheir friend, cousins, nephews.
OL,19,F"If you know who did this, then please
OL,20,Fsearch your conscience and help us.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774012289
OL,3,CFamily of murdered teenager vow to
OL,4,Cmatch #20,000 reward for information
OL,6,F"Don't assist these people, don't
OL,7,Fprotect them because if this could
OL,8,Fhappen to Ellis, then it could happen
OL,9,Fto another innocent child so they
OL,10,Fshouldn't be able to walk around the
OL,11,Fstreets.
OL,13,F"They've taken Ellis away from us and
OL,14,Fthey don't deserve to be living their
OL,15,Flife."
OL,17,FAny information can be provided
OL,18,Fdirectly and anonymously to the
OL,19,Fcharity in the hope it leads to the
OL,20,Fconviction of those responsible.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774012289
OL,3,CFamily of murdered teenager vow to
OL,4,Cmatch #20,000 reward for information
OL,6,FThe period of the Crimestoppers reward
OL,7,Fwas due to expire next month. But
OL,8,Fit'll now continue for the foreseeable
OL,9,Ffuture.
OL,11,FJulie O'Toole, Ellis' auntie said:
OL,12,F"Any information at all. No matter how
OL,13,Frelevant you think it may be or that
OL,14,Fthe police may have heard it before,
OL,15,Fjust please call. Let the police be
OL,16,Fthe judge of that."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
