PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774012289
OL,3,CFamily of murdered teenager vow to
OL,4,Cmatch #20,000 reward for information
OL,6,FShe added: "We have hope every day and
OL,7,Fhope in Merseyside Police and every
OL,8,Ffaith in them and I think with the
OL,9,Fincrease in #40,000, as a family we
OL,10,Fhave pulled together and he means that
OL,11,Fand everything more to us so we hope
OL,12,Fthe #40,000 does make a difference.
OL,14,F"Just dig deep and search your
OL,15,Fconscience to stop this happening to
OL,16,Fsomeone else."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
