PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774012289
OL,3,CFamily of murdered teenager vow to
OL,4,Cmatch #20,000 reward for information
OL,6,F"Our sole focus is to get justice for
OL,7,FEllis. I will never stop because they
OL,8,Ftook my baby away from me and we won't
OL,9,Fstop until they are behind bars," says
OL,10,FCarolyn.
OL,12,FTo give information anonymously,
OL,13,Fplease contact Crimestoppers on 0800
OL,14,F555 111.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
